# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Claude Code Authentication (Choose ONE method)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Option 1: OAuth Token (Recommended for Claude Pro/Max subscriptions)
# Best for: Production, high volume, predictable monthly costs
# How to get: Run "claude setup-token" on your local machine
# Format: sk-ant-oat01-...
# Benefits: Subscription rate limits (50K/day), priority access, ~$0.20-0.30/meeting
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-oat01-YOUR-TOKEN-HERE

# Option 2: API Key (For pay-as-you-go usage)
# Best for: Testing, low volume, variable usage
# How to get: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Format: sk-ant-api03-...
# Benefits: No monthly fee, pay only for usage, ~$0.30-0.50/meeting
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-YOUR-KEY-HERE

# Priority: CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN > ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
# Note: Set ONE method (OAuth token recommended if you have a subscription)

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Deployment Configuration (for surge.sh)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Surge.sh credentials (for Claude Code to deploy dashboards)
# Get token by running: surge token
SURGE_LOGIN=your_email@example.com
SURGE_TOKEN=your_surge_token_here
# Note: SURGE_EMAIL also works (for backwards compatibility)

